title: May I know why I can only see three of my rank 5 champs in my profile?
body: When I turn to the other page I can only see the ones I dont have rank 5 with, why dont the others appear besides the three champs I have with the highest score? Is it supposed to be like that?

replies.body: Thats just how it is man, If you go to your champs page you can see them all and even put them in order of mastery.
